{"tid":1775952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(5大訴求wfc) 林鄭 :  歇止暴力、 回復社會秩序是政府首要目標","createTime":"2019-12-09T07:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T10:42:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d5f81284ad3b048aec3b6561223567ea046eb4","tid":1775952,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:46:02.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥表示, 香港正經歷困難時刻, 但根基和制度優勢不會輕易動搖.<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥出席香港經濟峰會2020致辭時說, 今年香港經濟面對內憂外患不幸陷入衰退, 出口和零售及來港旅客數字大跌, 失業率預期會逐步上升, 企業開始倒閉, 財政預算將現赤字, 反映現時經濟情況嚴峻. 不過今年香港競爭力和世銀全球營商便利度排第三位, 上周的國際貨幣基金組織報告亦都顯示本港仍具制度優勢.<br />\n<br />\n至於昨日的遊行, 她認為大致和平有序, 但批評有少數暴徒針對法院進行破壞及縱火, 踐踏法治精神. <br />\n<br />\n她重申, 歇止暴力、 回復社會秩序是政府首要目標, 會以堅持一國兩制和法治作為應對目前社會狀況的原則. <br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsID=20191209150128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdefault.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20191209150128&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=65958c89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsID=20191209150128</a>"},{"pid":"5065789b0758edad32379eb3e7df4cd6be96a005","tid":1775952,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:47:52.000Z","msg":"聽咗好多次喇<br />\n有冇第二句<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614b3b6d5232e5741c0a9e37e208833a9ad04663","tid":1775952,"uid":66569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:50:49.000Z","msg":"止暴制亂到2047<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a4aff3f8c5783cf6e800f5e98000f2e5f6d664","tid":1775952,"uid":82628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"警暴是唯一的暴力"},{"pid":"74649030c5b00849526ff2e723ebc1052941f9c9","tid":1775952,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:42:09.000Z","msg":"其實關鍵在於佢自己點決定<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 借宣